<div>
  Hi <%= @order.first_name %>,
</div>
<br>
<div>
  Good news! Your Heartful.ly order has been successfully processed.
</div>
<br>  
<div>
  <%= @order.registry.name %> are being notified of your generous gift and note as you read this message.
</div>
<div>
  For your records, you purchased:
</div>
<div>
  <% order_summary(@order.summary).each do |item, quantity| %>
    <div><%= "#{item} (#{quantity}): " %> $<%= (@order.registry.item_types.where(name: item).first.price * quantity.to_i).to_i %></div>
  <% end %>
</div>
<br>
<div>
  What's next? On <%= @order.registry.name %>'s wedding day, the funds will be transferred to the organization leading this project. As the project gets underway, you will receive a few email updates from us. Think of it as an opportunity to watch the love grow! 
</div>
<br>
<div>
  Thanks for helping <%= @order.registry.name %> build love where it's needed most. 
</div>
<br>
<div>
  My Best,
  <br>
  Kate Glantz, Founder
  <br>
  Heartful.ly
</div>
<br>
<div>
  Questions about your order? Contact us any time at <%= mail_to "info@heartful.ly" %>. 
</div>